{"tid":1591681,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"兵法！暴政既存亡同社會運作既關係","createTime":"2019-09-24T09:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T10:09:13.000Z","uid":222614,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d175bb16389c60dc085f35f2e9876101532578be","tid":1591681,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:08:41.000Z","msg":"暴政等同惡疾，依賴社會運作維生，最終目的係消滅一個文化<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者其實早就意識到可以干擾社會運作既目標：立法會、機場等等，所以暴政先會傾全體制之力去保護脆弱既部位，亦係維持社會運作既必須手段<br />\n<br />\n持續罷工係最大威脅，因為社會基本上會停止運作，即使暴政手握世上最強既軍隊都控制唔到局面（無可能殺曬全部參與罷工既市民），去到一個臨界點之後，體制就會解散<br />\n<br />\n所以如果要救義士，持續罷工係最有效方法，唔洗咁多策略同核彈；停止社會運作就係最大既核彈"},{"pid":"9c29473a28ff00a2d99e91fcf68ec2f16df6ad3b","tid":1591681,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"宜設法停止社會運作"},{"pid":"78a760d26cbb672736cd260dce3ada41f6464b92","tid":1591681,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:10:30.000Z","msg":"大家要記住呀！！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">929反赤納粹行動</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全球呀！</span></strong></span><br />\n我地唔可以輸比世界上任何一個地區，我地幾咁憎赤納粹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求正虎黑警交代831，新屋嶺！要求了解被捕義士情況！求真相求解釋！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有仲有，唔好唔記得今個月大家有咩要做呀！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPoppm7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPoppm7.png&h=0935ebd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYT48OO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYT48OO.png&h=cc06dc40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推推推推推，p牌仔開唔到post唯有洗爆你地留言！"},{"pid":"0126f4fbb377a3f1e5f8603ab6ec6225ab476586","tid":1591681,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"Shut down the life supply to the totalitarian regime"},{"pid":"b9f52ea5453d7d346ac90002db11d0bf05df80c8","tid":1591681,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"暴政既生存指數，與社會運作既暢順度成正比"},{"pid":"23b93a04ea2e83099394e4520e4f9883bcc7baab","tid":1591681,"uid":117585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:23:37.000Z","msg":"絕對同意，只要罷工就可以停止運作<br />\n但諗多少少，停止左之後，會形成一個咩情況？<br />\n如果可以再諗埋之後會點，我相信更多人會願意罷工停止社會運作。"},{"pid":"a1456543a2fca7b92548d2bd2f55d16e24c080f1","tid":1591681,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:25:01.000Z","msg":"大家要記住呀！！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">929反赤納粹行動</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全球呀！</span></strong></span><br />\n我地唔可以輸比世界上任何一個地區，我地幾咁憎赤納粹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求正虎黑警交代831，新屋嶺！要求了解被捕義士情況！求真相求解釋！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有仲有，唔好唔記得今個月大家有咩要做呀！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPoppm7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPoppm7.png&h=0935ebd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYT48OO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYT48OO.png&h=cc06dc40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推推推推推，p牌仔開唔到post唯有洗爆你地留言！"},{"pid":"851cb9f98ce3dbfdaf737640fb46cc285796fd06","tid":1591681,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dis